titles.title: CB 133 Wonderful and Marveloous is Jesus to Me

verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
WONDERFUL AND MARVELOUS IS JESUS TO
ME.
Sweeter than the honey from the honeycomb is
He.
Jesus is real. He'll never fail.
I will praise Him now and throughout all eternity.
He is always with me as I'm walking along;
He has put His life in me and now I have a song.
Jesus is real ...
